00:06:37.950 --> 00:06:40.560
Oh ! C'est la fin de la fôret !

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:43.870
Très bien ! Allons directement à cacao island !

00:06:50.150 --> 00:06:52.040
Brook ! Chopper !

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:54.170
