00:13:03.740 --> 00:13:09.180
Mon gâteau de mariage !

00:13:09.180 --> 00:13:09.920
Oh, non !

00:13:12.820 --> 00:13:13.880
Esquivez !

00:13:21.080 --> 00:13:22.100
