sameigawara seiken jet bazooka

00:22:02.640 --> 00:22:03.580
yatta !

00:22:05.520 --> 00:22:07.110
Pas encore, pas encore...

00:22:07.460 --> 00:22:10.200
Ne me sous-estimez pas !

00:22:11.400 --> 00:22:12.920
Hein ? Qu'est-ce que c'est ?!

00:22:16.600 --> 00:22:18.700
Candy maiden

00:22:19.400 --> 00:22:21.050
decoration

00:22:21.830 --> 00:22:23.720
